The paper focuses on hardware acceleration of convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of FPGA-based solutions also falls under computer architecture (cs.AR) and digital circuits (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the optimization of the accelerator architecture, which could fall under control systems (cs.SY).
